## Use the following for enrolling into the RH network.

#### Register
Use the `subscription-manager register` to register your system to the RHN.

You will need your username and password

#### Available subscription list
`subscription-manager list --available --all`

#### Attach to the pool
`subscription-manager subscribe --pool=<pool id>`

#### Disable repos
`subscription-manager repos --disable=*`

This will disable all repos

#### Attaching subscriptions 

/usr/bin/subscription-manager repos --enable=rhel-7-server-rpms --enable=rhel-7-server-rh-common-rpms --enable=rhel-7-server-extras-rpms


#### Especially for CloudForms
`subscription-manager repos --enable=cf-me-5.5-for-rhel-7-rpms`
